A small map, the round will end probably in a minute or less.
Inspired by a ship in the SOCOM series on the ps2.

Ship is a map of a tiny cargo ship that is beginning to sink, hence the water on the lower level.

Uh, there is no restrictions on use, you can even claim it to be your (then to have your friends say you suck at mapping)

Someone said that there were textures missing, the secret ones, so i'll fix that in the final.
